{"tid":337334,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"當對方提出分手應該要點做？","createTime":"2017-07-27T08:27:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-27T10:24:15.000Z","uid":2538,"like":6,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"aafd3973588ed1eb2de40df4c5220df8f357d39d","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:27:16.000Z","msg":"當佢提出分手，但你又知佢立場唔多堅定仲有啲十五十六咁，應該點？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 應該不斷去比佢知道自己會為佢改，會等佢，唔會輕易放棄佢<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 直接唔搵佢，比空間佢諗清楚，如果係愛你既就會番黎你身邊"},{"pid":"0cc69bc128dc4a90b9f2aa3e01e7e39c2a6e2db3","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:40:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb31715faa5e5bc171a8e208ce338ad9fe2699ba","tid":337334,"uid":113227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:50:39.000Z","msg":"睇對方性格而異"},{"pid":"162217569366c4c9f063b09cb1e6707356448d5b","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T08:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇對方性格而異</blockquote><br />\n如果佢性格係一直好痴身，好無安全感好易呷醋。但平時又好有主見，每樣野都有自己睇法，講野好直，諗到乜就講乜。"},{"pid":"a8c44f43ef66323823d70b0203b967be3b1b84b8","tid":337334,"uid":131514,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:01:52.000Z","msg":"男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時女仔講分手都係想人氹<br />\n男就唔知 我成日無啦啦畀人飛<br />\n<br />\n利: 藍絲"},{"pid":"c1fe443754027a17d6f548cf9ee7e2fe276abae7","tid":337334,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:02:55.000Z","msg":"喊"},{"pid":"445d2da3d1d482f6ec6e50f5eaf6fbabe1ea1eef","tid":337334,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:03:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>喊</blockquote><br />\n啲女仔會覺得, 你為佢而喊就覺得佢對你好重要,就心軟<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"8702d4c43269a006102b724831818829edd55096","tid":337334,"uid":78971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:04:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇對方性格而異</blockquote><br />\n如果佢性格係一直好痴身，好無安全感好易呷醋。但平時又好有主見，每樣野都有自己睇法，講野好直，諗到乜就講乜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正評啦"},{"pid":"4a10c31b644e081f2cca0798fd84ebc865d1d2ff","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:06:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時女仔講分手都係想人氹<br />\n男就唔知 我成日無啦啦畀人飛<br />\n<br />\n利: 藍絲</blockquote><br />\n佢係女，佢從來未試過講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次突然咁樣，話想分開下諗清楚。我又衰，太驚會失去佢，哥幾日不斷同佢作出承諾想挽留佢，點知chur到佢好決絕咁講分手。"},{"pid":"2cb0afdafcc8afe3eb2c8a7c103047c3946d2b28","tid":337334,"uid":46020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>睇對方性格而異</blockquote><br />\n如果佢性格係一直好痴身，好無安全感好易呷醋。但平時又好有主見，每樣野都有自己睇法，講野好直，諗到乜就講乜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係咪我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己覺得呢種女仔需要你哄<br />\n如果你唔哄，扮絕情，佢唔會主動再痴埋黎因為佢覺得你唔愛佢"},{"pid":"8a9c3acecf9cab283d0990ad701a7d6c9b7e03eb","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:07:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>喊</blockquote><br />\n啲女仔會覺得, 你為佢而喊就覺得佢對你好重要,就心軟<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\n平時佢都會受呢套，但今次真係難講了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a1198902fc18be8f546032b36eb940d2280b9d9b","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:09:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇對方性格而異</blockquote><br />\n如果佢性格係一直好痴身，好無安全感好易呷醋。但平時又好有主見，每樣野都有自己睇法，講野好直，諗到乜就講乜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢個係咪我黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我自己覺得呢種女仔需要你哄<br />\n如果你唔哄，扮絕情，佢唔會主動再痴埋黎因為佢覺得你唔愛佢</blockquote><br />\n但分手後哥幾日我係咁搵佢，話我永遠唔會放棄，會為佢改。但佢只係不斷話太遲了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會唔會等佢番黎面對面講會好啲"},{"pid":"488d83ad720ed301bd1f367e6007f361fc80d6f4","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>睇對方性格而異</blockquote><br />\n如果佢性格係一直好痴身，好無安全感好易呷醋。但平時又好有主見，每樣野都有自己睇法，講野好直，諗到乜就講乜。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n正評啦</blockquote><br />\n但係佢點解可以完全唔搵我，我搵佢就hea覆，係咪真係需要時間冷靜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5dc7a31e1e0b3970bc3fe4ab49208314c23f1bf","tid":337334,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:11:09.000Z","msg":"頭也不回"},{"pid":"117b369da8807b78b8aa42fdb6873320921247ac","tid":337334,"uid":12429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:11:31.000Z","msg":"你衰咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a039f781bb211fc69ac378939b93a3142bd2c32","tid":337334,"uid":65578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:12:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea895400fbadde6a61bd285aa2a463e3be20ebf0","tid":337334,"uid":93282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:12:58.000Z","msg":"問清楚原因先"},{"pid":"1933a170a92241a22012df7283749a33f838d2d0","tid":337334,"uid":76577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:13:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>男定女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有時女仔講分手都係想人氹<br />\n男就唔知 我成日無啦啦畀人飛<br />\n<br />\n利: 藍絲</blockquote><br />\n佢係女，佢從來未試過講分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次突然咁樣，話想分開下諗清楚。我又衰，太驚會失去佢，哥幾日不斷同佢作出承諾想挽留佢，點知chur到佢好決絕咁講分手。</blockquote><br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">無事既</span><br />\nBtw哥你老母"},{"pid":"1146298db6c3cdadb80c25e1b45a88d80db6913d","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:14:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你衰咩先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話我呢年懶左，同埋講左咁多年既浪漫都比唔到佢，所以淡左。但佢前一晚先講完不如等佢番黎就同居，一齊努力維繫番段關係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點知第二日就話分開"},{"pid":"3763f6ded00a6f8192af036ed7980ea27fe771a6","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:16:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>問清楚原因先</blockquote><br />\n成件事得佢媽知，佢細佬幫我打探到佢有苦衷，當時都喊到七彩，但佢媽死唔肯講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8def537e7706dfbf2f03774b5b5677daf878914","tid":337334,"uid":2538,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:50:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>頭也不回</blockquote><br />\n感情太深，一時間好難做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78d6c29653322e64b76e52577e1df98c9ad26b61","tid":337334,"uid":114275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T09:56:52.000Z","msg":"有離心已經唔洗留 next"},{"pid":"54a5d7d5c0f487eabbd7cf602b89e15bc4dd875e","tid":337334,"uid":43825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-27T10:24:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>頭也不回</blockquote><br />\n感情太深，一時間好難做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁可能因為我短時間<br />\n諗清楚之後既然完左就算<br />\n因為呢個世界好大的"}]}